<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Et respondet: <hi rend="italic">in custodiendo <choice n="0.85"><sic n="2422">uerba</sic><corr n="410">ueri</corr></choice> t u a</hi>. et <lb/>
