            portare: ipse uos <choice><sic>baptizabitin</sic><corr>baptizabit</corr></choice> spiritu <lb/>
            sancto et igni: habet uentilabrum in manu <lb n="20"/>
            sua et permundabit aream suam et <sic n="poss">congre</sic>- <lb/>
