<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Itaque a tanto <choice n="0.06"><sic n="9">nolens</sic><corr n="138">uolens</corr></choice> crimine uindicare humanum genus <lb/>
