            obprobrio. non igitur corporis, sed cordis intellegenda est circumcisio. <lb n="5"/>
            si intellexeris legem, seruabis eam in corde tuo.</p></div>

<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="2"><p>Iudaeus in corde  <lb/>
