            deponit animam qui desiderat. si tamen spes propior <choice><sic>aasurgai</sic><corr>adsurgat</corr></choice>, <sic>uai</sic> <lb/>
            uires spes proxima, si autem absentia sit dilecti, eo ipso quod absentem <lb/>
