            in asperitate licet positus glaciali mortificauerit tamen corpus <sic>smUll</sic>, <lb/>
</p></div>

<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="2"><p>            ne sentiret hiemis illius asperitatem quam saluator dicit grauem <lb n="15"/>
