<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Imitatores etiam ipsius caelestis simus elementi: non semper <lb/>
            sole <choice><sic>feraet</sic><corr>feruet</corr></choice> ardenti, frequenter nubibus <choice n="0.74"><sic n="53">tegitur</sic><corr n="18">texitur</corr></choice>, pluuiis uehementibus <lb/>
