</p></div>

<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="2"><p>            ille taeterrimus, non unius Aegypti, sed saeculi istius princeps, uinculo  <lb/>
            seruitii grauis nos tenebat <choice><sic>adstnctos</sic><corr>adstrictos</corr></choice>. non obliuiscamur in aeternum, <lb/>
