</div>
<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p><choice><sic>Xunc</sic><corr>Nunc</corr></choice>, quia consummationis finem agnouimus, agnoscamus <lb/>
