            imago terreni, suscipiatur imago caelestis non <choice><sic>fnco</sic><corr>fuco</corr></choice> expressa, <choice n="0.00"><sic n="18">uon</sic><corr n="65020">non</corr></choice> <lb/>
            ceris, non coloribus adumbrata sed moribus, in qua se Christus <lb/>
            agnoscat. <lb n="25"/>
            
</p>
          
</div>
</div>
