<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Demonstrauit summam conclusionem nec <choice><sic>ulliun</sic><corr>ullum</corr></choice> remedium <lb/>
            nisi in aduentu domini nostri Iesu Christi, qui solus desperatis possit <lb/>
