            expectet, et miserationis diuinae suffragium poscit, ut in ea uiuificetur <lb/>
            a domino. non ergo adrogans debitae mercedis exactor, sed<lb n="15"/>
            uerecundus misericordiae diuinae est deprecator. 
</p>
          
</div>
</div>
<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
