<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Utinam ego talis esse merear, ut, si forte persecutor ingruerit, <lb/>
            non considerem suppliciorum meorum acerbitates, non metiar tormenta, <lb/>
            non poenas, non cogitem ullius atrocitatem doloris, sed haec<lb n="10"/>
            omnia leuia ducam, trepidem autem ne Christus me neget, <lb/>
            ne Christus excludat, ne me repellat de concilio sacerdotum, <lb/>
            si indignum eo collegio iudicauerit, uideat magis, licet permotum <lb/>
            corporalium terrore poenarum, plus tamen trepidantem futura <lb/>
            iudicia! etsi dixerit mihi: modicae fidei, quare<lb n="15"/>
            dubitasti?, porriget tamen dexteram et insurgentis fluctus saecularis <lb/>
            huius mole turbatum fida mentis statione firmabit. 
</p>
          
</div>
</div>
<div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1">
<div type="textpart" subtype="section" n="1">
<p>Sequitur uersus secundus: <hi rend="italic">e <sic>xulto</sic> in <choice n="0.00"><sic n="5">uerb</sic><corr n="1789">uerbis</corr></choice> <choice n="0.64"><sic n="3288">is</sic><corr n="1832">tuis</corr></choice> t uis,<lb/>
